{"tid":633712,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻敏感發作真係好絕望","createTime":"2018-04-18T14:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T10:56:14.000Z","uid":29601,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"92d5e8074bbe441dd805c5b9230d71b532324e11","tid":633712,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"好想死 完全係身心折磨<br />\n呢年好似特別嚴重<br />\n無啦啦又可以發作<br />\n流鼻水、鼻無時無刻痕、打乞、流眼水<br />\n包雲吞包到成座山咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人都俾佢搞到頹撚晒 咩都唔想做 <br />\n出到街你又係咁流鼻水 搭地鐵迫埋啲 啲人都歧視你<br />\n原本生活已經唔順意 加埋鼻敏感真係地獄般感受 前世做錯咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似除咗移民無咩方法完全根治 <br />\n天炙果啲我都做過幾輪 但無乜成效 <br />\n好似絕症咁 諗起成個人生都係要不停鼻敏感發作都頹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6d8ae6c503def6b0088c84920e939a4e2d7a5","tid":633712,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"噴藥啦"},{"pid":"e3df75d0d30c80653ea3bb512b892ff42a28d0c7","tid":633712,"uid":126255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"屌仲要次次開始溫書先嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e7d7b31bfac7e78a4ec790f07bfae5ea6fca5e","tid":633712,"uid":29601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e3df75d0d30c80653ea3bb512b892ff42a28d0c7","tid":633712,"uid":126255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"屌仲要次次開始溫書先嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"屌那星 我又係 真係準時間到仆街<br />\n要考試/ 交功課先嚟發作 工作效率大減"},{"pid":"2b6a434f98321d5fa340ac9109e9db791ade4c9c","tid":633712,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"我都發作緊，成日聞到一陣灰塵味<img s