99daaeda177b3d18bb1950a00ea0fee9e6f79802","tid":633712,"uid":359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"鼻入面腫左，氣都抖唔到<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要有鼻水流出黎<br />\n呻又呻唔到，吸又吸唔到<br />\n遲一秒啲鼻水已經可以滴出黎<br />\n勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690d1aedf8af194b70f24176c6f4e8cc94059fc6","tid":633712,"uid":127503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"唔好飲涷野<br />\n游水/跑步<br />\n有用"},{"pid":"c234bd4d693186e3602f52fbadd2cc034073aa2d","tid":633712,"uid":45763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"試吓噴鼻？之前都係鼻敏感，個鼻塞到抖唔到氣，買咗枝鼻眼適噴咗一星期左右好返好多，起碼瞓到覺。好似買咗$130，唔係間間藥房有"},{"pid":"e97a2521df821152d67786f186f7c97766fb2b96","tid":633712,"uid":70808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e18d7b0a5b40d22cc351f684759c242fb7a32d18","tid":633712,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac35498d657cac117ae9213db874ff0ff49763cc","tid":633712,"uid":70808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"其實你有無花粉敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感同花粉症唔係同一樣嘢嚟咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T23:46:12.000Z","msg":"花粉症可能會導致流鼻水和鼻塞<br />\n<br />\n鼻敏感係鼻對於某些環景/物件 過敏 如對塵,動物毛<br />\n<br />\n花粉症唔一定會鼻敏感<br />\n<br />\n有鼻敏感唔一定會有花粉"},{"pid":"e40d1e5c3f6ab4e7a70b53b7a4a7cbf2307e7d17","tid":633712,"uid":82540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"試下去買支生理鹽水洗鼻，每晚沖完涼洗，洗返半個月就差唔多好，我就係成功嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}